<bibRefCitation author="Froeschner, R. C." box="[1185,1378,1735,1761]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="544 - 607" refId="ref49613" refString="Froeschner, R. C. (1988) Family Pentatomidae Leach, 1815. The stink bugs. In: Henry, T. J. &amp; Froeschner, R. C. (Eds.), Catalog of the Heteroptera, or True Bugs, of Canada and the Continental United States. E. J. Brill, Leiden, New York, pp. 544 - 607. https: // doi. org / 10.1201 / 9781351070447 - 30" type="book chapter" year="1988">Froeschner 1988</bibRefCitation>
