<bibRefCitation author="Santos, B. T. S. dos &amp; da Silva, V. J. &amp; Fernandes, J. A. M." box="[151,371,1771,1798]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="445 - 470" refId="ref61385" refString="Santos, B. T. S. dos, da Silva, V. J. &amp; Fernandes, J. A. M. (2015) Revision of Ascra with proposition of the bifida species group and description of two new species (Hemiptera: Pentatomidae: Edessinae). Zootaxa, 4034 (3), 445 - 470. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4034.3.2" type="journal article" year="2015">
Santos 
<emphasis box="[233,289,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">et al.</emphasis>
(2015)
</bibRefCitation>
placed this species in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Say" authorityYear="1832" box="[735,800,1771,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Ascra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
